don't understand what happened to me.

291
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:43,710
I don't understand what happened to my mother.

292
00:19:43,710 --> 00:19:47,210
And I'm trying to read and learn things,but...

293
00:19:47,210 --> 00:19:49,600
mostly,I just...

294
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:52,230
I still feel lost.

295
00:19:52,230 --> 00:19:54,980
See,now you sound like a real 4400.

296
00:19:55,430 --> 00:19:58,130
