318
00:21:17,780 --> 00:21:19,900
There were no takers.

319
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:23,150
I guess no one wanted to cooperate
with the organization

320
00:21:23,150 --> 00:21:25,110
that was working to put you in prison.

321
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:28,710
We had to fight just to get them to let
us post agents outside their houses.

322
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:32,240
Crockett!
You ready to go for a walk,boy?

323
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,910
Come on,crockett.
Let's go.

324
00:21:34,910 --> 00:21:40,030
They wanted no part of us.They all seemed
confident that T.J. Kim was acting alone.Crockett?

325
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,890
What's wrong?

326
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:23,700
This arrived 15 minutes ago.

327
00:22:25,210 --> 00:22:27,250
This is a message from the nova group.

328
00:22:27,250 --> 00:22:30,130
We are the defensive wing of the 4400.

329
00:22:30,130 --> 00:22:33,870
Today,the world has seen what happens
to those who try to harm us.

330
00:22:33,870 --> 00:22:38,620
A second demonstration of our
capabilities is planned for october 19th.

331
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:41,850
- A new era dawns.
- Defensive wing,huh?

332
00:22:41,850 --> 00:22:43,690
What happens when they decide to play offense?

333
00:22:43,690 --> 00:22:46,510
- I guess we find out in five days.
- They didn't even say what they want.

334
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:48,180
No demands,no room for compromise.

335
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:51,310
We don't even know how many 4400s
are in this nova group.

336
00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:53,950
We couldn't even handle one when she
walked in and attacked the place.

337
00:22:53,950 --> 00:22:56,570
Now there's a whole team of assassins
out there,all with abilities?

338
00:22:56,570 --> 00:22:59,700
They've got someone who can kill
you by lowering your body temperature.

339
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:02,060
- Don't forget the beastmaster.
- What?

340
00:23:02,060 --> 00:23:03,830
That dog got pissed off pretty quick.

341
00:23:03,830 --> 00:23:07,770
Well,I've been all over the files,and none of
these abilities have been registered with us.

342
00:23:07,770 --> 00:23:11,960
They're off the inhibitor now.We can't even pretend
to have a comprehensive list of what these people can do.

343
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:15,800
Is anyone feeling...
a little overmatched here?

344
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:26,380
You two remember gary navarro?

345
00:23:27,590 --> 00:23:29,200
Hey,gary.

346
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:31,070
Been a while.

347
00:23:31,770 --> 00:23:33,720
You're right,baldwin.

348
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:35,770
I do think you two sold me out.

349
00:23:35,770 --> 00:23:39,700
It really bothered me for a while,but now I
understand it's just standard operating procedure.

350
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:42,490
Well,I guess that mind reading
thing is working pretty well,huh?

351
00:23:42,490 --> 00:23:43,780
Better than ever,actually.

352
00:23:43,780 --> 00:23:47,850
Gary's telepathic abilities have been
very useful to the national security agency.

353
00:23:47,850 --> 00:23:50,640
They have agreed to let us borrow him
while we investigate the nova group.

354
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,110
So you're clear on what we're doing here?

355
00:23:52,110 --> 00:23:55,040
You want to use a 4400 to track down other 4400s.

356
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:57,040
- Do you have a problem with that?
- Not at all.

357
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:59,370
It won't be my first time.

358
00:24:00,190 --> 00:24:02,610
So...
can we get started?

359
00:24:07,180 --> 00:24:10,330
Never heard of the nova group.xxxxxxxxxx

360
00:24:10,330 --> 00:24:14,460
xxxxxxxxxxxx

361
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:18,510
xxxxxxxxxx Between ntac and this place,

362
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:20,460
but I trust you realize how serious this is.

363
00:24:20,460 --> 00:24:23,320
Believe me,if I knew anything,I would tell you.

364
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:26,810
Well,do you mind if the three of us walk
around the place,talk to some people?

365
00:24:26,810 --> 00:24:29,550
You and your pet mind-reader?
No,I can't let you do that.

366
00:24:29,550 --> 00:24:32,500
These people haven't done anything wrong,
and I won't let you invade their privacy,

367
00:24:32,500 --> 00:24:36,370
and I actually can't believe that
you brought this guy here again.

368
00:24:36,370 --> 00:24:40,430
How much do they pay you to spy on
your own kind?Getting a clear signal?

369
00:24:40,430 --> 00:24:43,350
You see anything you like up there?

370
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:47,810
As far as I can tell,he's not hiding anything.

371
00:24:48,620 --> 00:24:51,820
I have a lot of work to do.
If I hear anything,I'll give you a call.

372
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:54,410
For now,that's the best I can do.

373
00:25:05,650 --> 00:25:07,640
Sorry about my nephew.

374
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:08,430
Why?

375
00:25:08,430 --> 00:25:10,220
Well,he was kind of rude back there.

376
00:25:10,220 --> 00:25:12,960
I get that kind of stuff a lot.
I don't take it personally.

377
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:14,250
Do you mind if I ask you...

378
00:25:14,250 --> 00:25:17,970
you've sort of implied that you've
pursued 4400s in the past.

379
00:25:17,970 --> 00:25:20,160
What exactly do you do for the nsa?

380
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,930
Overseas stuff,mostly.

381
00:25:21,930 --> 00:25:23,970
But,like,what?
Give me an example.

382
00:25:23,970 --> 00:25:25,700
They fly me someplace.

383
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:28,570
I approach the subject,
find out what he's thinking,

384
00:25:28,570 --> 00:25:32,580
and I tell the people i work for,who then
fly me home,where I live comfortably.

385
00:25:32,580 --> 00:25:35,440
What happens to the subject?

386
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:39,360
I don't ask.

387
00:25:49,650 --> 00:25:51,000
That's good.

388
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:53,610
The neural pathway comparisons
are particularly illuminating.

389
00:25:53,610 --> 00:25:55,960
Make sure you understand them
before you move on.

390
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:58,950
Dr. Burkhoff,I don't understand any of this.

391
00:25:58,950 --> 00:26:01,640
A bunch of her neurons don't work anymore.

392
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:04,410
Every time one of hers turns off,
one of mine turns on.

393
00:26:04,410 --> 00:26:05,900
Exactly...

394
00:26:05,900 --> 00:26:10,690
and what's true for neurons is
true for muscle fibers,synaptic pathways...

395
00:26:10,690 --> 00:26:12,060
there is A...

396
00:26:12,060 --> 00:26:18,110
one-to-one correspondence between the
amount you lost and the amount you gained.

397
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:20,640
So all this is just a way of saying
I'm doing this to her?

398
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:24,140
