restored to her normal self.

404
00:26:41,410 --> 00:26:43,760
- The aging agent?
- He means me.

405
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:48,090
I'm killing you.The only way for you
to live is for me to die,isn't that right?

406
00:26:48,090 --> 00:26:53,370
Don't answer that,dr. Burkhoff.
Thank you for your time.We're done here.

407
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:55,870
Where are you going?

408
00:26:56,210 --> 00:26:58,690
We're not discussing this.

409
00:26:58,690 --> 00:27:01,920
Not now.Not ever.

410
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:12,950
- It's true,isn't it?
- I think so.

411
00:27:19,060 --> 00:27:21,540
But it's only a theory.

412
00:27:22,750 --> 00:27:25,020
Guys,I went over this six weeks
ago with the men in black.

413
00:27:25,020 --> 00:27:26,190
Humor us.

414
00:27:26,190 --> 00:27:29,550
I went on two dates with T.J. Kim.
I cut it off.

415
00:27:29,550 --> 00:27:31,500
- Girl had a lot of baggage.
