419
00:27:37,650 --> 00:27:40,410
I would've taken notes,

420
00:27:40,410 --> 00:27:42,530
hey,so listen...

421
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:46,420
all this stuff about october 19th...
you guys think it's serious?

422
