464
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:30,150
Turn around.
Turn around.

465
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:37,130
- We done here?
- Get out of here.

466
00:30:39,910 --> 00:30:43,800
Call me sensitive,
but I felt like saying to him,

467
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:47,480
