468
00:30:51,190 --> 00:30:55,790
You guys just don't really get it,do you?
It's not just that guy.

469
00:30:55,790 --> 00:30:59,400
Every 4400
we've talked to today,they're scared of you,

470
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:01,640
